The following 3 commands are used to generate the xml/html documents:

1 Read the dll library and generate the xml document directory.
$monodocer  -assembly:clronep/bin/Release/clronep.dll -path:xmldocs -pretty

2 Edit the documents. 
$monodoc --edit xmldocs

3 Transform to html files 
$mdoc export-html -o docs xmldocs


This link has detail information:

http://www.mono-project.com/Generating_Documentation#Assemble_the_generated_Documentation
